OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport reopens with delays
OL,4,Cafter 'suspicious package' found
OL,6,FEdinburgh Airport has reopened after
OL,7,Fparts of the terminal building were
OL,8,Fevacuated on Friday due to a security
OL,9,Falert, but passengers have been warned
OL,10,Fof delays to services.
OL,12,FAn explosive ordnance disposal team
OL,13,Fwas deployed to the airport to
OL,14,Finvestigate what Police Scotland
OL,15,Fdescribed as a "potentially suspicious
OL,16,Fpackage" discovered at around 6.50pm
OL,17,Fon Friday.
OL,19,FAn evacuation was ordered and a police
OL,20,Fcordon was set up, with roads closed.
OL,26,@wD@POUxD@HO]
