OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport reopens with delays
OL,4,Cafter 'suspicious package' found
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FPassengers faced disruption as result
OL,12,Fof the operation, and the airport
OL,13,Fwarned that its schedules would
OL,14,Fcontinue to be affected by the
OL,15,Fincident on Saturday.
OL,17,FIn a statement at around 3am on
OL,18,FSaturday morning, the airport
OL,19,Fconfirmed it had reopened and would
OL,20,Fwork to restore normal services as
OL,21,Fquickly as possible.
