OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport reopens with delays
OL,4,Cafter 'suspicious package' found
OL,6,F"Following investigations by
OL,7,Fspecialist teams, the airport has now
OL,8,Freopened," the airport said.
OL,10,F"We recognise the frustration this
OL,11,Fincident will have caused and thank
OL,12,Feveryone for their patience and
OL,13,Funderstanding ` safety will always
OL,14,Fcome first.
OL,16,F"This incident will have knock-on
OL,17,Fimpacts throughout today and staff are
OL,18,Fworking hard to address these and
OL,19,Fsupport passengers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@JO]rD@AOUxD@AOU
