OL,3,CEdinburgh Airport reopens with delays
OL,4,Cafter 'suspicious package' found
OL,6,F"Operational teams are continuing to
OL,7,Fwork to restore normal services as
OL,8,Fquickly as possible.
OL,10,F"Please check with your airline for
OL,11,Fthe latest information on your flight."
OL,13,FThe statement did not provide an
OL,14,Fupdate on the examination of the
OL,15,Fsuspicious package.
